ce use may be more intense in more areas marked by seasonal climatic variations. Specifically, a larger size in seasonal areas may allow individuals to explore a wider niche. We suggest that future approaches, refining regional variation in the diet of C. villosum may serve as a further test to this hypothesis.", "access_right": "restricted", "creators": [{"name": "Siniciato\u00a0Terra\u00a0Garbino, Guilherme", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Ant\u00f4nio, Daphne Chiara", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Da Cunha\u00a0Tavares, Val\u00e9ria", "affiliation": null}], "keywords": ["Biodiversity", "Mammalia", "Chiroptera", "Chordata", "Animalia", "bats", "bat"], "related_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/3c18559c6700b5222103ae851ecb6c55", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://sha256/d68bd26e9553780d6d96f8fe68bd4618a9bf5c8afe3cb8f571b493d80e94a5ef", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "zotero://select/groups/5435545/items/S5AYPP8X", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://zotero.org/groups/5435545/items/S5AYPP8X", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://linker.bio/cut:hash://md5/69e95b507e02af6f43bed8030aa7f1ca!/b286991-289512", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://md5/330417efcaa2560c9b8ebcd6fae17ce0", "relation": "isPartOf", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "10.5281/zenodo.1410543", "relation": "isCompiledBy", "resource_type": "software", "scheme": "doi"}], "custom": {"dwc:class": ["Mammalia"], "dwc:kingdom": ["Animalia"], "dwc:order": ["Chiroptera"], "dwc:phylum": ["Chordata"]}, "resource_type": {"title": "Journal article", "type": "publication", "subtype": "article"}, "journal": {"issue": "3", "pages": "552-562", "title": "Austral Ecology", "volume": "48"}, "alternate_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/3c18559c6700b5222103ae851ecb6c55"}, {"identifier": "urn:lsid:zotero.org:groups:5435545:items:S5AYPP8X"}, {"id